data.description: Welcome to 7036 Marsden St, a charming twin home that effortlessly combines classic aesthetics with modern comforts.  As you approach this residence, you are greeted by an inviting sun parlor enclosed porch, complete with a handy closet. Step inside to discover a spacious living room, anchored by an authentic brick fireplace that promises cozy evenings. The kitchen boasts wooden cabinets that provide ample storage and are outfitted with a relatively new gas range and dishwasher, ensuring meal preparation is both enjoyable and convenient.  The home also accommodates three generously sized bedrooms, each with its own character, airy and welcoming with ceiling fans and great closet space.  Further adding to the home's amenities is a full basement with a full-bathroom, driveway, and backyard deck.  7036 Marsden St is more than just a house—it's a place to create lasting memories, offering space, character, and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful Philadelphia gem your new home.
